        </div>
        
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Todo es posible</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Dentro de nosotros está toda la capacidad</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Todo resultado es mejorable</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>El amor es vida y esencia de la existencia</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>La paz es la madre de la sanación</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>La alegría es el motor</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>El propósito es la dirección</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>El amor al prójimo nutre la existencia</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Somos consciencia eterna y parte del todo</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>El poder sanador sobre nosotros mismos aumenta cuánto más nos amamos</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>El desarrollo de todo sistema o comunidad aumenta por acción de un ser flexible que fomenta el amor, la consciencia y la autorresponsabilidad</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Somos seres dimensionales de libre albedrío</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>La coherencia consciente es indispensable para sostener la vida</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Somos más libres cuando asumimos la propia responsabilidad de nosotros mismos</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Eficacia y Estadísticas inspirado en index.astro -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition-all hover:shadow-2xl mb-16">
        <div class="p-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400">
          <div class="bg-white p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <span class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400 text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Eficacia y Resultados</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">97%</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Eficacia comprobada en el tratamiento de enfermedades graves</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-teal-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-2">30</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Años de experiencia en medicina alternativa integrativa</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">60.000+</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Personas atendidas, capacitadas y mejoradas</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Nuestra metodología ha demostrado resultados extraordinarios en patologías como:
              </p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Cáncer</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Enfermedades crónicas</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Enfermedades autoinmunes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>Dolores crónicos</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="/casos-exito" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400 text-white rounded-lg hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-teal-500 transition-all duration-300 font-medium shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105">
